FT  13 NOV 92 / International Company News: Arthur Andersen lifts revenue by
13% worldwide
ARTHUR ANDERSEN, the accounting and consulting firm, announced revenues up
13 per cent to Dollars 5.57bn for the year to August 31.
Andersen, which employs more than 62,000 staff worldwide, lifted revenues by
9 per cent to Dollars 2.96bn in the Americas, 16 per cent to Dollars 2.14bn
in Europe, Middle East, India and Africa, and 16 per cent to Dollars 1.84bn
in Asia/Pacific.
